405
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:26,830
Apa ini?

406
00:30:30,310 --> 00:30:32,820
<i>Lee Dam, Pihak A mulai sekarang.</i>

407
00:30:34,660 --> 00:30:37,350
<i>Shin Woo-Yeo, Pihak B mulai sekarang.</i>

408
00:30:37,740 --> 00:30:40,560
Pihak B wajib menjaga keselamatan A
dan Kelereng A,

409
00:30:40,650 --> 00:30:43,070
